### Get all rentals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentals
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get all active rentals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rentals/active
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Rent
