}

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Add role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{kamilId}}/roles/add?
    roleName=ADMIN
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Remove role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{kamilId}}/roles/remove?
    roleName=USER
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

